width: 0px; height: 1.969em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.897em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 2.652em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mfrac><msubsup><mi mathvariant="normal">T</mi><mn>2</mn><mn>2</mn></msubsup><msubsup><mi mathvariant="normal">T</mi><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></msubsup></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><msubsup><mi mathvariant="normal">R</mi><mn>2</mn><mn>3</mn></msubsup><msubsup><mi mathvariant="normal">R</mi><mn>1</mn><mn>3</mn></msubsup></mfrac><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">T</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mo>=</mo><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">T</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo>×</mo><msup><mrow><mo>(</mo><mfrac><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">R</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">R</mi><mn>1</mn></msub></mfrac><mo>)</mo></mrow><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mn>3</mn><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mo>/</mo></mrow><mn>2</mn></mrow></msup><mo>=</mo><mn>365</mn><mo>×</mo><msup><mrow><mo>(</mo><mfrac><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">R</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mrow><mn>2</mn><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">R</mi><mn>1</mn></msub></mrow></mfrac><mo>)</mo></mrow><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mn>1.5</mn></mrow></msup><mo>=</mo><mn>129</mn><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mi mathvariant="normal">d</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">a</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">y</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">s</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-18">\rm \frac{T_2^2}{T_1^2}=\frac{R_2^3}{R_1^3}\Rightarrow T_2=T_1\times\left(\frac{R_2}{R_1}\right)^{3/2}=365\times\left(\frac{R_1}{2R_1}\right)^{1.5}=129\ days </script></span></p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
<div class="row questionBlock">

                            <div class="row question">
                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial"><span>Question 2</span></div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p>পৃথিবীতে&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-6-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mn>365</mn><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>d</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>a</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>y</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-88" style="width: 6.298em; top: -2.234em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-89"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-90" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">365</span><span class="mtext" id="MathJax-Span-91" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">&nbsp;</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-92" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">d</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-93" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">a</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-94" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">y</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-95" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; </span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div><div class="row questionBlock">

width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="font-family: MathJax_Main; position: absolute; top: -4.014em; left: 4.305em;">−<span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(2.748em, 1001.03em, 4.797em, -999.998em); top: -4.137em; left: 0em;"><span style="font-family: MathJax_Size2;">√</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-634" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-635" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">223</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.969em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -1.198em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 3.052em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mfrac><msubsup><mi mathvariant="normal">T</mi><mn>2</mn><mn>2</mn></msubsup><msubsup><mi mathvariant="normal">T</mi><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></msubsup></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><msubsup><mi mathvariant="normal">R</mi><mn>2</mn><mn>3</mn></msubsup><msubsup><mi mathvariant="normal">R</mi><mn>1</mn><mn>3</mn></msubsup></mfrac><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">T</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mo>=</mo><msqrt><msubsup><mi mathvariant="normal">T</mi><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></msubsup><mo>×</mo><mfrac><msubsup><mi mathvariant="normal">R</mi><mn>2</mn><mn>3</mn></msubsup><msubsup><mi mathvariant="normal">R</mi><mn>1</mn><mn>3</mn></msubsup></mfrac></msqrt><mo>=</mo><msqrt><msup><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mn>365</mn></mrow><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>×</mo><msup><mrow><mo>(</mo><mfrac><mn>54</mn><mn>75</mn></mfrac><mo>)</mo></mrow><mn>3</mn></msup></msqrt><mo>=</mo><mn>223</mn></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-34">\rm \frac{T_2^2}{T_1^2}=\frac{R_2^3}{R_1^3}\Rightarrow T_2=\sqrt{T_1^2\times\frac{R_2^3}{R_1^3}}=\sqrt{{365}^2\times\left(\frac{54}{75}\right)^3}=223 </script></span></p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div><div class="row questionBlock">

                            <div class="row question">
                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial"><span>Question 4</span></div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p>কোনো নক্ষত্রের চতুর্দিকে পরিভ্রমণরত একটি গ্রহের দুটি ভিন্ন সময়ের বেগ যথাক্রমে&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit;                                                 <label style="margin-left:5px;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-6-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mn>12</mn><mo>:</mo><mn>23</mn></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-46" style="width: 3.463em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 2.826em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.414em, 1002.78em, 2.37em, -999.998em); top: -2.229em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-47"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-48" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">12</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-49" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.276em;">:</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-50" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.276em;">23</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.234em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.053em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 0.947em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mn>12</mn><mo>:</mo><mn>23</mn></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-6">12:23 </script></span></p>
</label>
                                                
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                    <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">
                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p>কেপলারের সূত্র অনুযায়ী,&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-7-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><msup><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>T</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>&amp;#x221D;</mo><msup><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>r</mi><mn>3</mn></msup><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>&amp;#x21D2;</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>T</mi></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>k</mi><msup><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>r</mi><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mfrac><mn>3</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac></mrow></msup></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-51" style="width: 9.305em; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.383em; left: 0.74em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-55" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.969em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.747em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 2.103em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mi mathvariant="normal">v</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>2</mn><mi>π</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">r</mi></mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">T</mi></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>π</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">r</mi><mo>.</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">k</mi><mo>.</mo><msup><mi mathvariant="normal">r</mi><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mo>−</mo><mfrac><mn>3</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac></mrow></msup><mo>=</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>π</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">k</mi><msup><mi mathvariant="normal">r</mi><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mo>−</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac></mrow></msup><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">v</mi><mo>∝</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><msqrt><mi mathvariant="normal">r</mi></msqrt></mfrac></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-8">\rm v=\frac{2\pi r}{T}=2\pi r.k.r^{-\frac{3}{2}}=2\pi kr^{-\frac{1}{2}}\Rightarrow v\propto\frac{1}{\sqrt r}</script></span>&nbsp;</p>

</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row questionBlock">

                            <div class="row question">
                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial"><span>Question 5</span></div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p>একটি স্প্রিংয়ের উপর 5N বল প্রয়োগে 2J স্থিতিশক্তি সঞ্চিত হলে স্প্রিংয়ের সংকোচন কত?&nbsp;</p>

                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="row questionOptions">
                                    <div class="col-sm-12 row questionOption">
                                        <div class="input-group" style="align-items: center;">
                                            <div class="input-group-prepend">
                                                <span class="input-group-text">A</span>

                                    <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">
                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-17-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>W</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>F</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>x</mi><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>&amp;#x21D2;</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>2</mn><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mn>2</mn></mrow><mn>5</mn></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>0.8</mn><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>m</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>80</mn><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>c</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>m</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-187" style="width: 17.256em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 14.141em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.986em, 1014.14em, 2.461em, -999.998em); top: -1.965em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-188"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-189" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">W</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-190" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mfrac" id="MathJax-Span-191" style="padding-left: 0.289em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.494em; height: 0px; margin-right: 0.125em; margin-left: 0.125em;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1000.29em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.424em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.162em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-192" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">1</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1000.33em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -3.645em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.162em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-193" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.904em, 1000.49em, 1.191em, -999.998em); top: -1.268em; left: 0em;"><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: 0em; border-top: 1.5px solid; width: 0.494em; height: 0px;"></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mtext" id="MathJax-Span-194" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">&nbsp;</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-195" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">F</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-196" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">x</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-197" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">⇒</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-198" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">x</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-199" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mfrac" id="MathJax-Span-200" style="padding-left: 0.289em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.395em; height: 0px; margin-right: 0.125em; margin-left: 0.125em;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1001.23em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.424em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.613em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-201"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-202" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-203" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">×</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-204" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1000.33em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -3.645em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.162em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-205" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">5</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.904em, 1001.39em, 1.191em, -999.998em); top: -1.268em; left: 0em;"><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: 0em; border-top: 1.5px solid; width: 1.395em; height: 0px;"></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-206" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-207" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">0.8</span><span class="mtext" id="MathJax-Span-208" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">&nbsp;</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-209" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">m</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-210" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; width: 0px; height: 1.969em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.497em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.602em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mi mathvariant="normal">W</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mi mathvariant="normal">F</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">x</mi><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">x</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>2</mn><mo>×</mo><mn>2</mn></mrow><mn>5</mn></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>0.8</mn><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mi mathvariant="normal">m</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>80</mn><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mi mathvariant="normal">c</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">m</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-17">\rm W=\frac{1}{2}\ Fx\Rightarrow x=\frac{2\times2}{5}=0.8\ m=80\ cm </script></span></p>
</span>
                                    </div>

                                        <div class="serial"><span>Question 6</span></div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p>পৃথিবীর ভর অপরিবর্তিত থাকলে এবং ব্যাসার্ধ হঠাৎ অর্ধেক হয়ে গেলে বিষুব রেখায় অভিকর্ষজ ত্বরণের মান কত হবে?</p>

                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>

<p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-23-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>&amp;#x21D2;</mo><msub><mi>&amp;#x03C9;</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mo>=</mo><mn>4</mn><msub><mi>&amp;#x03C9;</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo>=</mo><mn>2.91</mn><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><msup><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mn>10</mn></mrow><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>4</mn></mrow></msup><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>r</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>a</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>d</mi><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mo>/</mo></mrow><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>s</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-291" style="width: 14.182em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 11.6em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.986em, 1011.56em, 2.338em, -999.998em); top: -1.965em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-292"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-293" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">⇒</span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-294" style="padding-left: 0.289em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.068em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1000.62em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-295" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">ω</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -3.85em; left: 0.617em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-296" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-297" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-298" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">4</span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-299"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.068em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1000.62em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-300" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">ω</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -3.85em; left: 0.617em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-301" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">1</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-302" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-303" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">2.91</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-304" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">×</span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-305" style="padding-left: 0.207em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.969em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.24em, 1000.95em, 4.182em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="texatom" id="MathJax-Span-306"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-307"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-308" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">10</span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.424em; left: 0.986em;"><span class="texatom" id="MathJax-Span-309"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-310"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-311" style="font-size: 70.7%; width: 0px; height: 1.969em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.348em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.453em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><msub><mi>ω</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mo>=</mo><mn>4</mn><msub><mi>ω</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo>=</mo><mn>2.91</mn><mo>×</mo><msup><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mn>10</mn></mrow><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mo>−</mo><mn>4</mn></mrow></msup><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mi mathvariant="normal">r</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">a</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">d</mi><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mo>/</mo></mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">s</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-23">\rm \Rightarrow\omega_2=4\omega_1=2.91\times{10}^{-4}\ rad/s</script></span>&nbsp;</p>

<p>ব্যাসার্ধ অর্ধেক হলে,&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-24-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><msup><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>g</mi><mi class=&quot;MJX-variant&quot;                                         </div>

padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1470" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">421.875</span><span class="mtext" id="MathJax-Span-1471" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">&nbsp;</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1472" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">W</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.969em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.497em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 2.202em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">P</mi><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mi mathvariant="normal">o</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">u</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">t</mi></mrow></msub><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mi mathvariant="normal">I</mi><msup><mi>ω</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></mrow><mn>50</mn></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>4</mn></mfrac><mi mathvariant="normal">m</mi><msup><mi mathvariant="normal">r</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><msup><mi>ω</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></mrow><mn>50</mn></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>421.875</mn><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mi mathvariant="normal">W</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-99">\rm P_{out}=\frac{\frac{1}{2}I\omega^2}{50}=\frac{\frac{1}{4}mr^2\omega^2}{50}=421.875\ W</script></span>&nbsp;[কাজ শক্তি উপপাদ্য ব্যবহারে কৃতকাজ বের করা হয়েছে।]</p>

<p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-100-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2234;</mo><mi>&amp;#x03B7;</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>P</mi><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>o</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>u</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>t</mi></mrow></msub><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>P</mi><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>i</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>n</mi></mrow></msub></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>421.875</mn><mn>500</mn></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>84.375</mn><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>&amp;#x0025;</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1473" style="width: 13.445em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 11.027em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.068em, 1010.99em, 2.789em, -999.998em); padding-left: 0.289em;">η<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.002em;"></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1477" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mfrac" id="MathJax-Span-1478" style="padding-left: 0.289em;"><span style="display: inline-block; margin-left: -0.613em;"><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-1479"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.273em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.404em, 1000.45em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1480" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">P</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; font-family: MathJax_Main;">P</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -3.891em; left: 0.494em;"><span class="texatom" id="MathJax-Span-1488"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1489"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1490" style="font-size: 50%; </span>
                                    </div>

                                    <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">
                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p>ভরবেগ&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-106-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mn>100</mn><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>&amp;#x0025;</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1519" style="width: 2.379em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.928em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.109em, 1001.89em, 2.133em, -999.998em); top: -1.965em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1520"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1521" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">100</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1522" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">%</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.969em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.098em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.103em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mn>100</mn><mi mathvariant="normal">%</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-106">100\%</script></span>&nbsp;বৃদ্ধি পাওয়া মানে দ্বিগুণ হওয়া।&nbsp;</p>

<p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-107-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2235;</mo><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>E</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>k</mi></msub><mo>&amp;#x221D;</mo><msup><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>P</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>&amp;#x2234;</mo></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1523" style="width: 5.822em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 4.756em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.232em, 1004.72em, 2.461em, -999.998em); top: -2.17em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1524"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1525" style="font-family: MathJax_AMS;">∵</span><span class="mtext" id="MathJax-Span-1526" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">&nbsp;</span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-1527"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.15em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.199em, 1000.66em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1528" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">E</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -3.85em; left: 0.699em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1529" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">k</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1530" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">∝</span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-1531" style="padding-left: 0.289em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.109em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.199em, 1000.62em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1532" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">P</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.383em; left: 0.699em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1533" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1534" style="font-family: MathJax_AMS; padding-left: 0.289em;">∴</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.174em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.247em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.302em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mo>∵</mo><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">E</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">k</mi></msub><mo>∝</mo><msup><mi mathvariant="normal">P</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>∴</mo></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-107">\rm \because\ E_k\propto P^2  \therefore </script></span>&nbsp;গতিশক্তি 4&nbsp;গুণ হবে বা&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-108-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mn>300</mn><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>&amp;#x0025;</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1535" style="width: 2.379em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.928em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.109em, 1001.89em, 2.133em, -999.998em); top: -1.965em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1536"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1537" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">300</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1538" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">%</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.969em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.098em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.103em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mn>300</mn><mi mathvariant="normal">%</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-108">300\%</script></span>&nbsp;বৃদ্ধি পাবে।&nbsp;</p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-31-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>E</mi><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mo>&amp;#x221D;</mo><msup><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>P</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-416" style="width: 3.404em; top: -1.965em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-417"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-418" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">E</span><span class="mtext" id="MathJax-Span-419" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">&nbsp;</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-420" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">∝</span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-421" style="padding-left: 0.289em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.109em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.199em, 1000.62em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-422" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">P</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.383em; left: 0.699em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-423" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.969em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.048em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.153em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mi mathvariant="normal">E</mi><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mo>∝</mo><msup><mi mathvariant="normal">P</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-31">\rm E\ \propto P^2</script></span>&nbsp;; তাই, গতিশক্তি&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-32-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mn>300</mn><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>&amp;#x0025;</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-424" style="width: 2.625em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 2.133em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.109em, 1002.09em, 2.133em, -999.998em); top: -1.965em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-425"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-426" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">300</span><span class="mtext" id="MathJax-Span-427" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">&nbsp;</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-428" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">%</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.969em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.098em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.103em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mn>300</mn><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mi mathvariant="normal">%</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-32">300\ \% </script></span>&nbsp;বাড়লে বা <span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit;                             <div class="row question">
                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial"><span>Question 10</span></div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p>&nbsp;70kg&nbsp;ভরের একজন ব্যক্তি&nbsp;10m&nbsp;দীর্ঘ মই বেয়ে উপরে উঠেন। মইটি ভূমির সাথে&nbsp;75°&nbsp;কোণে হেলানো থাকলে, ব্যক্তি দ্বারা কৃতকাজ কত?</p>

                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-35-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>W</mi><mo>=</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>F</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>x</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>c</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>o</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>s</mi><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mo>&amp;#x3B8;</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mn>70</mn><mo>&amp;#xD7;</mo><mn>9.8</mn><mo>&amp;#xD7;</mo><mn>10</mn><mo>&amp;#xD7;</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>c</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>o</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>s</mi><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>(</mo><msup><mn>90</mn><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>o</mi></msup><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><msup><mn>75</mn><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>o</mi></msup><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>)</mo><mo>=</mo><mn>6626</mn><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>J</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-436" style="width: 23.65em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 19.387em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.109em, 1019.35em, 2.338em, -999.998em); top: -1.965em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-437"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-438" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">W</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-439" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-440" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">F</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-441" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">x</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-442" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">c</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-443" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">o</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-444" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">s</span><span class="texatom" id="MathJax-Span-445"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-446"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-447" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">θ</span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-448" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">×</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-453" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">10</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-454" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">×</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-455" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">c</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-456" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">o</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-457" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">s</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-458" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">(</span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-459"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.436em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.24em, 1000.95em, 4.182em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-460" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">90</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.424em; left: 0.986em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-461" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">o</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-462" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">−</span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-463" style="padding-left: 0.207em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.436em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.24em, 1000.95em, 4.182em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-464" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">75</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.424em; left: 0.986em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-465" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">o</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-466" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">)</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-467" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; width: 0px; height: 1.969em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.348em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.302em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mi mathvariant="normal">W</mi><mo>=</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">F</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">x</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">c</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">o</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">s</mi><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mo>θ</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mn>70</mn><mo>×</mo><mn>9.8</mn><mo>×</mo><mn>10</mn><mo>×</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">c</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">o</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">s</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><msup><mn>90</mn><mi mathvariant="normal">o</mi></msup><mo>−</mo><msup><mn>75</mn><mi mathvariant="normal">o</mi></msup><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mo>=</mo><mn>6626</mn><mi mathvariant="normal">J</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-35">\rm W=Fxcosθ=70×9.8×10×cos(90^o-75^o)=6626J</script></span></p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row questionBlock">

                            <div class="row question">
                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial"><span>Question 11</span></div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p>একটি পানিপূর্ণ কুয়ার গভীরতা ও ব্যাসার্ধ যথাক্রমে&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-36-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mn>10</mn><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi>m</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-470" style="width: 2.61em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 2.126em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.455em, 1002.09em, 2.386em, -999.998em); width: 0px; height: 2.237em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.089em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 0.911em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mn>10</mn><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mi>m</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-36">10\ m</script></span>&nbsp;ও <span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit;                                         <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-42-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>P</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>W</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>t</mi></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>m</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>g</mi><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mfrac><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>h</mi><mn>2</mn></mfrac></mrow><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>t</mi></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi>&amp;#x03C0;</mi><msup><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>r</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>l</mi><mi>&amp;#x03C1;</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>g</mi><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mfrac><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>h</mi><mn>2</mn></mfrac></mrow><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>t</mi></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>3.14</mn><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><msup><mn>2</mn><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mn>10</mn><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><msup><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mn>10</mn></mrow><mn>3</mn></msup><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mn>9.8</mn><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mn>5</mn></mrow><mrow><mn>20</mn><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mn>60</mn><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mn>746</mn></mrow></mfrac><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>H</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>P</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>6.87</mn><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>H</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>P</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-504" style="width: 26.969em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 22.092em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.494em, 1022.05em, 2.461em, -999.998em); top: -1.965em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-505"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-506" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">P</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-507" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mfrac" id="MathJax-Span-508" style="padding-left: 0.289em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.863em; height: 0px; margin-right: 0.125em; margin-left: 0.125em;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.404em, 1000.7em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.424em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.367em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-509" style="font-size: 70.7%; </span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row questionBlock">

                            <div class="row question">
                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial"><span>Question 12</span></div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p>প্যারাবলিক (Parabolic) পথে পৃথিবী পৃষ্ঠ ছেড়ে চলে যেতে হলে কোনো বস্তুর নিক্ষেপ বেগের শর্ত-</p>

                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial"><span>Question 13</span></div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p>হাইপারবলিক (Hyperbolic) পথে কোনো নিক্ষিপ্ত বস্তু পৃথিবী ছেড়ে চলে গেলে নিক্ষেপ বেগ ও মুক্তিবেগের সম্পর্ক কীরূপ হবে?</p>

</label>
                                                
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

<p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-48-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2234;</mo><mfrac><msub><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>V</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>e</mi></msub></mrow><mn>1</mn></msub><msub><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>V</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>e</mi></msub></mrow><mn>2</mn></msub></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>R</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>R</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></mfrac><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><msqrt><mfrac><msub><mi>&amp;#x03C1;</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><msub><mi>&amp;#x03C1;</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></mfrac></msqrt><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>&amp;#x21D2;</mo><mfrac><mn>2</mn><mn>3</mn></mfrac><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mo>=</mo><msqrt><mfrac><msub><mi>&amp;#x03C1;</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><msub><mi>&amp;#x03C1;</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></mfrac></msqrt><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>&amp;#x21D2;</mo><msub><mi>&amp;#x03C1;</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo>:</mo><msub><mi>&amp;#x03C1;</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>:</mo><mn>9</mn></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-643" style="width: 23.609em; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -3.85em; left: 0.535em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-704" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-705" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-706" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">1</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-707" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">:</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-708" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">9</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.174em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.897em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 2.302em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mo>∴</mo><mfrac><msub><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">V</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">e</mi></msub></mrow><mn>1</mn></msub><msub><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">V</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">e</mi></msub></mrow><mn>2</mn></msub></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">R</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">R</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></mfrac><mo>×</mo><msqrt><mfrac><msub><mi>ρ</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><msub><mi>ρ</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></mfrac></msqrt><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><mfrac><mn>2</mn><mn>3</mn></mfrac><mo>×</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mo>=</mo><msqrt><mfrac><msub><mi>ρ</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><msub><mi>ρ</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></mfrac></msqrt><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><msub><mi>ρ</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo>:</mo><msub><mi>ρ</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>:</mo><mn>9</mn></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-48">\rm \therefore\frac{{V_e}_1}{{V_e}_2}=\frac{R_1}{R_2}\times\sqrt{\frac{\rho_1}{\rho_2}}\Rightarrow\frac{2}{3}\times\frac{1}{2}=\sqrt{\frac{\rho_1}{\rho_2}}\Rightarrow\rho_1:\rho_2=1:9</script></span></p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>

                                    <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">
                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-90-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>V</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>e</mi></msub><mo>=</mo><msqrt><mn>2</mn><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>g</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>R</mi></msqrt><mo>=</mo><msqrt><mn>2.</mn><mfrac><mn>4</mn><mn>3</mn></mfrac><mi>&amp;#x03C0;</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>G</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>e</mi><msup><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>R</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></msqrt><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>&amp;#x21D2;</mo><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>V</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>e</mi></msub><mo>&amp;#x221D;</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>R</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1362" style="width: 16.928em; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -3.85em; left: 0.74em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1366" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">e</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 1.764em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; font-family: MathJax_Main; top: -4.014em; left: -0.08em;">−<span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; font-family: MathJax_Main; top: -4.014em; left: 1.068em;">−<span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="font-family: MathJax_Main; position: absolute; top: -4.014em; clip: rect(2.748em, 1001.03em, 4.797em, -999.998em); top: -4.055em; left: 0em;"><span style="font-family: MathJax_Size2;">√</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1386" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -3.85em; left: 0.74em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1389" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">e</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1390" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">∝</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1391" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">R</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.969em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.797em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 2.302em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">V</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">e</mi></msub><mo>=</mo><msqrt><mn>2</mn><mi mathvariant="normal">g</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">R</mi></msqrt><mo>=</mo><msqrt><mn>2.</mn><mfrac><mn>4</mn><mn>3</mn></mfrac><mi>π</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">G</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">e</mi><msup><mi mathvariant="normal">R</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></msqrt><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">V</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">e</mi></msub><mo>∝</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">R</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-90">\rm V_e=\sqrt{2gR}=\sqrt{2.\frac{4}{3}\pi Ge R^2}\Rightarrow V_e\propto R </script></span></p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="row questionBlock">

                            <div class="row question">
                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial"><span>Question 16</span></div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p style="text-align: justify;">পৃথিবীপৃষ্ঠ থেকে মুক্তিবেগ <span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-1-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mn>11.2</mn><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>k</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>m</mi><msup><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>s</mi><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msup></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1" style="width: 5.814em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 4.771em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.306em, 1004.77em, 2.349em, -999.998em); width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.609em, 1001.03em, 3.895em, -999.998em); top: -4.752em; left: 0.986em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.027em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; font-family: MathJax_Main; top: -4.014em; left: -0.08em;">−<span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; font-family: MathJax_Main; top: -4.014em; left: 0.33em;">−<span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.035em, 1001.03em, 4.51em, -999.998em); top: -4.219em; left: 0em;"><span style="font-family: MathJax_Size1;">√</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-109" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">×</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-110" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">11.2</span><span class="mtext" id="MathJax-Span-111" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">&nbsp;</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-112" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">k</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-113" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">m</span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-114"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.355em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1000.37em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-115" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">s</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.383em; left: 0.412em;"><span class="texatom" id="MathJax-Span-116"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-117"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-118" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">−</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-119" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">1</span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-120" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-121" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">33.6</span><span class="mtext" id="MathJax-Span-122" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">&nbsp;</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-123" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">k</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-124" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">m</span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-125"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.355em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1000.37em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-126" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">s</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.383em; left: 0.412em;"><span class="texatom" id="MathJax-Span-127"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-128"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-129" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">−</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-130" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">1</span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.592em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -2.998em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 4.452em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">V</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">e</mi></msub><mo>=</mo><msqrt><mn>2</mn><mi mathvariant="normal">g</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">R</mi></msqrt><mo>=</mo><msqrt><mn>2</mn><mo>×</mo><mfrac><mn>4</mn><mn>3</mn></mfrac><mi>π</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">R</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">G</mi><mi>ρ</mi><mo>×</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">R</mi></msqrt><mspace linebreak="newline"></mspace><mo>∴</mo><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">V</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">e</mi></msub><mo>∝</mo><msqrt><msup><mi mathvariant="normal">R</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mi>ρ</mi></msqrt><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mo>;</mo><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">V</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">x</mi></msub><mo>=</mo><msqrt><msup><mn>3</mn><mn>2</mn></msup></msqrt><mo>×</mo><mn>11.2</mn><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mi mathvariant="normal">k</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">m</mi><msup><mi mathvariant="normal">s</mi><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msup><mo>=</mo><mn>33.6</mn><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mi mathvariant="normal">k</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">m</mi><msup><mi mathvariant="normal">s</mi><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msup></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-6">\rm V_e=\sqrt{2gR}=\sqrt{2\times\frac{4}{3}\pi RG\rho\times R} \\ \therefore V_e\propto\sqrt{R^2\rho}\ ;V_x=\sqrt{3^2}\times11.2\ kms^{-1}=33.6\ kms^{-1} </script></span></p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>


                        <div class="row questionBlock">

                            <div class="row question">
                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial"><span>Question 17</span></div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p style="text-align: justify;">পৃথিবীপৃষ্ঠ থেকে মুক্তিবেগ <span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-28-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mn>11.2</mn><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>k</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>m</mi><msup><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>s</mi><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msup><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mo>;</mo></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-436" style="width: 6.485em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 5.292em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.306em, 1005.22em, 2.535em, -999.998em); top: -2.234em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-437"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-438" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">11.2</span><span class="mtext" id="MathJax-Span-439" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">&nbsp;</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-440" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">k</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-441" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">m</span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-442"><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 3.988em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.357em; left: 0.412em;"><span class="texatom" id="MathJax-Span-444"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-445"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-446" style="font-size: 70.7%; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.383em; left: 0.412em;"><span class="texatom" id="MathJax-Span-560"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-561"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-562" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">−</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-563" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">1</span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-564" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-565" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">5.6</span><span class="mtext" id="MathJax-Span-566" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">&nbsp;</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-567" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">k</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-568" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">m</span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-569"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.355em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1000.37em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-570" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">s</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.383em; left: 0.412em;"><span class="texatom" id="MathJax-Span-571"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-572"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-573" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">−</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-574" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">1</span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 5.617em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -4.197em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 5.752em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">V</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">e</mi></msub><mo>=</mo><msqrt><mn>2</mn><mi mathvariant="normal">g</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">R</mi></msqrt><mo>=</mo><msqrt><mn>2</mn><mi mathvariant="normal">g</mi><mo>×</mo><mfrac><mi mathvariant="normal">g</mi><mrow><mfrac><mn>4</mn><mn>3</mn></mfrac><mi>π</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">G</mi><mi>ρ</mi></mrow></mfrac></msqrt><mo>∴</mo><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">V</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">e</mi></msub><mo>∝</mo><msqrt><mfrac><msup><mi mathvariant="normal">g</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mi>ρ</mi></mfrac></msqrt><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mo>;</mo><mspace linebreak="newline"></mspace><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">V</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">x</mi></msub><mo>=</mo><msqrt><msup><mrow><mo>(</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mo>)</mo></mrow><mn>2</mn></msup></msqrt><mo>×</mo><mn>11.2</mn><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mi mathvariant="normal">k</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">m</mi><msup><mi mathvariant="normal">s</mi><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msup><mo>=</mo><mn>5.6</mn><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mi mathvariant="normal">k</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">m</mi><msup><mi mathvariant="normal">s</mi><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msup></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-33">\rm V_e=\sqrt{2gR}=\sqrt{2g\times\frac{g}{\frac{4}{3}\pi G\rho}}\therefore V_e\propto\sqrt{\frac{g^2}{\rho}}\ ; \\
V_x=\sqrt{\left(\frac{1}{2}\right)^2}\times11.2\ kms^{-1}=5.6\ kms^{-1}  </script></span></p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div><div class="row questionBlock">

                            <div class="row question">
                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial"><span>Question 18</span></div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p>সমান অভিকর্ষজ ত্বরণের দুটি গ্রহের ব্যাসার্ধের অনুপাত <span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-119-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mn>3</mn><mo>:</mo><mn>5</mn></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1531" style="width: 2.2em;                             <div class="row question">
                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial"><span>Question 19</span></div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p>সমান অভিকর্ষজ ত্বরণের দুটি গ্রহের ব্যাস যথাক্রমে 4000 km ও 2000 km। প্রথম গ্রহের পৃষ্ঠে মুক্তিবেগ&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-46-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mn>7.5</mn><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi>k</mi><mi>m</mi><msup><mi>s</mi><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msup></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-743" style="width: 5.367em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 4.398em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.306em, 1004.4em, 2.386em, -999.998em); top: -2.234em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-744"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-745" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">7.5</span><span class="mtext" id="MathJax-Span-746" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">&nbsp;</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-747" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">k</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-748" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">m</span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-749"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.455em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.43em, 1000.41em, 4.1em, -999.998em); top: -3.985em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-750" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">s</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 3.988em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.357em; left: 0.486em;"><span class="texatom" id="MathJax-Span-751"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-752"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-753" style="font-size: 70.7%;                                     <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">
                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-51-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>V</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>e</mi></msub><mo>&amp;#x221D;</mo><msqrt><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>R</mi></msqrt><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mo>;</mo><mfrac><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>V</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>V</mi><mn>1</mn></msub></mfrac><mo>=</mo><msqrt><mfrac><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>R</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>R</mi><mn>1</mn></msub></mfrac></msqrt><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>&amp;#x21D2;</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>15</mn><msqrt><mn>2</mn></msqrt></mrow><mn>4</mn></mfrac><mo>=</mo><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>V</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-815" style="width: 15.822em;                                     <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">
                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-51-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>P</mi><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>o</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>u</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>t</mi></mrow></msub><mo>=</mo><mn>100</mn><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mn>9.8</mn><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mn>15</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>14.7</mn><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>k</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>W</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-722" style="width: 14.264em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 11.682em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.15em, 1011.68em, 2.256em, -999.998em); top: -1.965em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-723"><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-724"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.764em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; </span>

                            </div>
                        </div>
