                                    <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">
                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p>গড় সরণ&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-58-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>=</mo></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-795" style="width: 0.822em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.658em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.477em, 1000.62em, 1.969em, -999.998em);                                                 <span class="input-group-text" style="font-weight:bold;">D</span>

                                    <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">
                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-43-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi>w</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>&amp;#x222B;</mo><mi>F</mi><mi>d</mi><mi>s</mi><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mo>;</mo><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mfrac><mrow><mi>d</mi><mi>s</mi></mrow><mrow><mi>d</mi><mi>t</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>2</mn><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>&amp;#x21D2;</mo><mi>d</mi><mi>s</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>d</mi><mi>t</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-653" style="width: 14.305em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 11.723em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.027em, 1011.68em, 2.543em, -999.998em); top: -2.047em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-654"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-655" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">w</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-656" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-657" style="font-family: MathJax_Size1; vertical-align: 0em; padding-left: 0.289em;">∫<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.125em;"></span></span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-658" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic; padding-left: 0.166em;">F<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.125em;"></span></span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-659" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">d<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.002em;"></span></span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-660" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">s</span><span class="mtext" id="MathJax-Span-661" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">&nbsp;</span><span class="mtext" id="MathJax-Span-662" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">&nbsp;</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-663" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">;</span><span class="mtext" id="MathJax-Span-664" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; margin-left: -0.367em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-667"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-668" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">d<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.002em;"></span></span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-669" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">s</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.404em, 1000.62em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -3.645em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.326em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-670"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-671" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">d<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.002em;"></span></span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-672" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">t</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; padding-left: 0.289em;">⇒</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-676" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic; padding-left: 0.289em;">d<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.002em;"></span></span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-677" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">s</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-678" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-679" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">2</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-680" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">d<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.002em;"></span></span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-681" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">t</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.051em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.497em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.652em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mi>w</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>∫</mo><mi>F</mi><mi>d</mi><mi>s</mi><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mo>;</mo><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mfrac><mrow><mi>d</mi><mi>s</mi></mrow><mrow><mi>d</mi><mi>t</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>2</mn><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><mi>d</mi><mi>s</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>d</mi><mi>t</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-43">w=\int Fds\ \ ;\ \ \frac{ds}{dt}=2\Rightarrow ds=2dt</script></span></p>

<p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-44-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>&amp;#x21D2;</mo><mi>w</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>&amp;#x222B;</mo><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mn>2</mn><mi>t</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mn>2</mn><mi>d</mi><mi>t</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>&amp;#x222B;</mo><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mn>4</mn><mi>t</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>2</mn></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mi>d</mi><mi>t</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-682" style="width: 15.535em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 12.707em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.109em, 1012.67em, 2.461em, -999.998em); top: -2.047em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-683"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-684" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">⇒</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-685" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic; padding-left: 0.289em;">w</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-686" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-687" style="font-family: MathJax_Size1; vertical-align: 0em; padding-left: 0.289em;">∫<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.125em;"></span></span><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-688" style="padding-left: 0.166em;"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-689" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">(</span><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-690"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-691" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-692" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">t</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-693" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.166em;">2</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-697" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">d<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.002em;"></span></span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-698" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">t</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-699" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-700" style="font-family: MathJax_Size1; vertical-align: 0em; padding-left: 0.289em;">∫<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.125em;"></span></span><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-701" style="padding-left: 0.166em;"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-702" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">(</span><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-703"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-704" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">4</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-705" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">t</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-706" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">+</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-707" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">2</span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-708" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">)</span></span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-709" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic; padding-left: 0.166em;">d<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.002em;"></span></span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-710" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">t</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.051em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.398em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.453em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><mi>w</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>∫</mo><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mn>2</mn><mi>t</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mn>2</mn><mi>d</mi><mi>t</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>∫</mo><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mn>4</mn><mi>t</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>2</mn></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mi>d</mi><mi>t</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-44">\Rightarrow w=\int\left(2t+1\right)2dt=\int\left(4t+2\right)dt</script></span></p>

<p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-45-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>=</mo><msubsup><mrow><mo>[</mo><mrow><mn>2</mn><msup><mi>t</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>t</mi></mrow><mo>]</mo></mrow><mn>0</mn><mn>3</mn></msubsup><mo>=</mo><mn>2</mn><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mn>9</mn><mo>+</mo><mn>2</mn><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mn>3</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>18</mn><mo>+</mo><mn>6</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>24</mn><mi>J</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-711" style="width: 19.674em; vertical-align: -0.547em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.852em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mo>=</mo><msubsup><mrow><mo>[</mo><mrow><mn>2</mn><msup><mi>t</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>t</mi></mrow><mo>]</mo></mrow><mn>0</mn><mn>3</mn></msubsup><mo>=</mo><mn>2</mn><mo>×</mo><mn>9</mn><mo>+</mo><mn>2</mn><mo>×</mo><mn>3</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>18</mn><mo>+</mo><mn>6</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>24</mn><mi>J</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-45">=\left[2t^2+2t\right]_0^3=2\times9+2\times3=18+6=24J</script></span></p>
</span>

<div class="row questionBlock">

                            <div class="row question">
                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial"><span>Question 24</span></div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-69-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>F</mi><mo>=</mo><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>(</mo><mn>4</mn><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>t</mi><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>)</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>N</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-917" style="width: 5.33em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 4.361em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.38em, 1004.32em, 2.61em, -999.998em); top: -2.234em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-918"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-919" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">F</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-920" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;                                         <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>

width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-971" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-972" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; <p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-77-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>=</mo><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mo>&amp;#x222B;</mo><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mn>4</mn><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>t</mi><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>d</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>t</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>4.</mn><msubsup><mrow><mo>[</mo><mfrac><msup><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>t</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mo>]</mo></mrow><mn>0</mn><mn>5</mn></msubsup><mo>=</mo><mn>2</mn></mrow><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>(</mo><mn>25</mn><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>0</mn><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>)</mo><mo>=</mo><mn>50</mn><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>J</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-988" style="width: 16.969em;                                             <p>একটি কৃত্রিম উপগ্রহ পৃথিবী &nbsp;পৃষ্ঠের কাছ দিয়ে ঘুরছে। এটিকে অসীমে পাঠাতে হলে এর গতি বাড়াতে হবে-</p>

                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p>পৃথিবী পৃষ্ঠের কাছ দিয়ে ঘুরলে&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-150-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi>v</mi><mo>=</mo><msqrt><mi>g</mi><mi>R</mi></msqrt></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-3848" style="width: 4.1em; width: 1.273em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; font-family: MathJax_Main; top: -4.014em; left: -0.08em;">−<span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; অসীমে পাঠাতে হলে অতিক্রান্ত বেগ,&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-151-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><msub><mi>v</mi><mi>e</mi></msub><mo>=</mo><msqrt><mn>2</mn><mi>g</mi><mi>R</mi></msqrt></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-3856" style="width: 5.002em;                                         <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-85-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>v</mi><mo>=</mo><msqrt><mfrac><mrow><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>G</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>M</mi></mrow><mrow><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>R</mi><mo>+</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>h</mi></mrow></mfrac></msqrt><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>&amp;#x21D2;</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>h</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>1587.4</mn><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>k</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>m</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1085" style="width: 12.666em; <p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-86-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2234;</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>T</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>2</mn><mi>&amp;#x03C0;</mi><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>R</mi><mo>+</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>h</mi></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow></mrow><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>v</mi></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>7088.46</mn><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>s</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>1.969</mn><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>h</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>o</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>u</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>r</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1106" style="width: 17.133em; padding-left: 0.289em;">7088.46</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1125" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">s</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1126" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1127" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">1.969</span><span class="mtext" id="MathJax-Span-1128" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">&nbsp;</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1129" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">h</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1130" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">o</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1131" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">u</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1132" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">r</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.174em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.497em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.852em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mo>∴</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">T</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>2</mn><mi>π</mi><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">R</mi><mo>+</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">h</mi></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow></mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">v</mi></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>7088.46</mn><mi mathvariant="normal">s</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>1.969</mn><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mi mathvariant="normal">h</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">o</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">u</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">r</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-86">\rm \therefore T=\frac{2\pi\left(R+h\right)}{v}=7088.46s=1.969\ hour</script></span></p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row questionBlock">

</label>

                                </div>
                                    <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">
                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>

                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p>কার্যকরী ক্ষমতা,&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-103-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>P</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>300</mn><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mn>0.8</mn><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>W</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>240</mn><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>W</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1306" style="width: 11.395em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 9.346em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.15em, 1009.35em, 2.133em, -999.998em); top: -1.965em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1307"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1308" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">P</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1309" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1310" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">300</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1311" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">×</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1312" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">0.8</span><span class="mtext" id="MathJax-Span-1313" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">&nbsp;</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1314" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">W</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1315" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1316" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">240</span><span class="mtext" id="MathJax-Span-1317" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">&nbsp;</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1318" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">W</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; <p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-104-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2234;</mo></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1319" style="width: 0.658em;                                     <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial"><span>Question 30</span></div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-121-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mn>0.1</mn><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi>k</mi><mi>g</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1744" style="width: 3.094em; position: relative; width: 1.969em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.24em, 1000.95em, 4.182em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="texatom" id="MathJax-Span-1834"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1835"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1836" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">10</span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.424em; left: 0.986em;"><span class="texatom" id="MathJax-Span-1837"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1838"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1839" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">−</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1840" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">3</span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mtext" id="MathJax-Span-1841" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">&nbsp;</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1842" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">J</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.969em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.497em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 2.052em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mi mathvariant="normal">E</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><msup><mi mathvariant="normal">p</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mrow><mn>2</mn><mi mathvariant="normal">m</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><msup><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mn>0.02</mn></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mn>2</mn></msup><mrow><mn>2</mn><mo>×</mo><mn>0.1</mn></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>2</mn><mo>×</mo><msup><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mn>10</mn></mrow><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mo>−</mo><mn>3</mn></mrow></msup><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mi mathvariant="normal">J</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-127">\rm E=\frac{p^2}{2m}=\frac{\left(\ 0.02\right)^2}{2\times0.1}=2\times{10}^{-3}\ J</script></span></p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                                    <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">
                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-112-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>E</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>k</mi></msub><mo>=</mo><mfrac><msup><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>p</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mrow><mn>2</mn><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>m</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>&amp;#x21D2;</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>p</mi><mo>=</mo><msqrt><mn>2</mn><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>m</mi><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>E</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>k</mi></msub></msqrt><mo>=</mo><msqrt><mn>2</mn><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mn>5</mn><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mn>70</mn></msqrt><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>k</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>g</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>m</mi><msup><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>s</mi><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msup><mo>=</mo><mn>26.46</mn><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>k</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>g</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>m</mi><msup><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>s</mi><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msup></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1415" style="width: 27.83em;                                         <div class="serial"><span>Question 32</span></div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p>20 টি ইটের প্রতিটির উচ্চতা <span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-113-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mn>6</mn><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi>c</mi><mi>m</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1468" style="width: 2.498em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 2.051em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.455em, 1002.01em, 2.386em, -999.998em); top: -2.234em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1469"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1470" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">6</span><span class="mtext" id="MathJax-Span-1471" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">&nbsp;</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1472" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">c</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1473" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">m</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.237em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.089em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 0.911em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mn>6</mn><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mi>c</mi><mi>m</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-113">6\ cm</script></span>। তাদের একটির ওপর আরেকটি রেখে একটি স্তম্ভ তৈরি করতে কৃতকাজ কত? [প্রতিটি ইটের ভর 1kg]&nbsp;</p>

                                                <label style="margin-left:5px;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-87-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mn>0.66</mn><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi>J</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1313" style="width: 3.281em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 2.689em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.414em, 1002.69em, 2.37em, -999.998em); top: -2.229em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1314"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1315" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">0.66</span><span class="mtext" id="MathJax-Span-1316" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">&nbsp;</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1317" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">J<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.093em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.234em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.053em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 0.947em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mn>0.66</mn><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mi>J</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-87">0.66\ J </script></span></p>
</label>
                                                
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="col-sm-12 row questionOption">
                                        <div class="input-group " style="align-items: center;">
                                            <div class="input-group-prepend">
                                                <span class="input-group-text" style="font-weight:bold;">D</span>
                                            </div>
                                            <div class="input-group-append questionTable">
                                                <label style="margin-left:5px;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-88-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mn>1.225</mn><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi>J</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1318" style="width: 3.918em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 3.19em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.414em, 1003.19em, 2.37em, -999.998em); top: -2.229em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1319"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1320" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">1.225</span><span class="mtext" id="MathJax-Span-1321" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">&nbsp;</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1322" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">J<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.093em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.234em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.053em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 0.947em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mn>1.225</mn><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mi>J</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-88">1.225\ J </script></span></p>
</label>
                                                
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                    <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">
                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p>দন্ডটির ভারকেন্দ্র এর মধ্যবিন্দুতে অবস্থিত হবে।&nbsp;</p>

<p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-89-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>w</mi><mo>=</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>m</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>g</mi><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mn>1</mn><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>c</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>o</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>s</mi><mi>&amp;#x03B8;</mi></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mn>0.5</mn><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mn>9.8</mn><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>c</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>o</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>s</mi><msup><mn>30</mn><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>o</mi></msup><mo>=</mo><mn>0.328</mn><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>J</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1323" style="width: 25.33em; top: -1.965em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1324"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1325" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">w</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1326" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.497em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.602em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mi mathvariant="normal">w</mi><mo>=</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">m</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">g</mi><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mn>1</mn><mo>−</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">c</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">o</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">s</mi><mi>θ</mi></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mn>0.5</mn><mo>×</mo><mn>9.8</mn><mo>×</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mo>×</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>−</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">c</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">o</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">s</mi><msup><mn>30</mn><mi mathvariant="normal">o</mi></msup><mo>=</mo><mn>0.328</mn><mi mathvariant="normal">J</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-89">\rm w=mg\frac{1}{2}\left(1-cos\theta\right)=0.5\times9.8\times\frac{1}{2}\times1-cos30^o=0.328J</script></span></p>
</span>

height: 1px; width: 0.002em;"></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1687" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.276em;">=</span><span class="mfrac" id="MathJax-Span-1688" style="padding-left: 0.276em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.458em; height: 0px; margin-right: 0.139em; margin-left: 0.139em;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.372em, 1000.32em, 4.146em, -999.998em); top: -4.415em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.18em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1689" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">4</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.01em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.418em, 1000.32em, 4.146em, -999.998em); top: -3.641em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.18em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1690" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">3</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.01em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.867em, 1000.46em, 1.186em, -999.998em); top: -1.273em; left: 0em;"><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: 0em; border-top: 1.3px solid; width: 0.458em; height: 0px;"></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.05em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mtext" id="MathJax-Span-1691" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">&nbsp;</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1692" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">π<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.002em;"></span></span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1693" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">ρ</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1694" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">R</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1695" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">G</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.234em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.497em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.669em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mi>g</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>4</mn><mn>3</mn></mfrac><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mi>π</mi><mi>ρ</mi><mi>R</mi><mi>G</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-129">g=\frac{4}{3}\ \pi\rho RG </script></span></p>
</label>
                                                
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                    <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">
                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-130-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi>V</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi>G</mi><mi>M</mi></mrow><mi>R</mi></mfrac></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1696" style="width: 4.633em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 3.773em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.945em, 1003.77em, 2.461em, -999.998em); top: -1.965em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1697"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1698" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">V<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.207em;"></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1699" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1700" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">−</span><span class="mfrac" id="MathJax-Span-1701"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.436em; height: 0px; margin-right: 0.125em; margin-left: 0.125em;"><span style="position: absolute; font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">G</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1704" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">M<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.043em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.404em, 1000.53em, 4.141em, -999.998em); height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.904em, 1001.44em, 1.191em, -999.998em); top: -1.268em; left: 0em;"><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: 0em; border-top: 1.5px solid; width: 1.436em; height: 0px;"></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.969em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.497em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.652em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mi>V</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>−</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi>G</mi><mi>M</mi></mrow><mi>R</mi></mfrac></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-130">V=-\frac{GM}{R} </script></span></p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div><div class="row questionBlock">

                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                    <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">

                            <div class="row question">
                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial"><span>Question 41</span></div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p style="text-align: justify;">একটি স্প্রিং এর সাথে যুক্ত একটি বস্তু কোনো আনুভূমিক তলের উপর দিয়ে চলাচল করতে পারে। বস্তুটি যখন <span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-14-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>x</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>i</mi></msub><mo>=</mo><mn>0.1</mn><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>m</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-220" style="width: 5.143em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 4.212em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.455em, 1004.21em, 2.498em, -999.998em); clip: rect(3.43em, 1000.52em, 4.1em, -999.998em); top: -3.985em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-223" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">x</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 3.988em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -3.836em; left: 0.523em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-224" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">i</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 3.988em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-225" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.263em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-226" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-15-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>x</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>f</mi></msub><mo>=</mo><mn>0.5</mn><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>m</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-228" style="width: 5.255em; top: -2.234em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-229"><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-230"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.859em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.43em, 1000.52em, 4.1em, -999.998em); top: -3.985em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-231" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">x</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px;                                         <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>

স্প্রিং বল দ্বারা কৃতকাজ&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-22-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>k</mi><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><msubsup><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>x</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>i</mi><mn>2</mn></msubsup><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><msubsup><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>x</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>f</mi><mn>2</mn></msubsup></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-281" style="width: 6.518em; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-318" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">−</span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-319" style="padding-left: 0.207em;"><span style="display: inline-block; &nbsp;</p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row questionBlock">

                            <div class="row question">
                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial"><span>Question 42</span></div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p>একটি বস্তুকে ভূমির সাথে 30° কোণে আনত তল বরাবর <span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-131-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mn>12</mn><mi>N</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1706" style="width: 2.275em;                                         <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-137-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>W</mi><mo>=</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>F</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>x</mi><mi>cos</mi><mo>&amp;#x2061;</mo><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mi>&amp;#x03B8;</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>12</mn><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mn>60</mn><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mi>cos</mi><mo>&amp;#x2061;</mo><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><msup><mn>0</mn><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>o</mi></msup><mo>=</mo><mn>720</mn><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>J</mi></mrow></mrow></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1734" style="width: 17.502em; top: -1.965em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1762"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1763" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">x</span></span><span style="display: inline-block;                             <div class="row question">

                                        <div class="serial"><span>Question 43</span></div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p>70kg&nbsp;ভরের একজন ব্যক্তি&nbsp;10m&nbsp;দীর্ঘ মই বেয়ে উপরে উঠেন। মইটি ভূমির সাথে&nbsp;75°&nbsp;কোণে হেলানো থাকলে, ব্যক্তি দ্বারা কৃতকাজ কত?</p>

                                                <label style="margin-left:5px;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-146-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mn>553.19</mn><mi>N</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1799" style="width: 4.51em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 3.691em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.414em, 1003.69em, 2.37em, -999.998em); top: -2.229em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1800"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1801" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">553.19</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1802" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">N<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.093em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.234em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.053em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 0.947em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mn>553.19</mn><mi>N</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-146">553.19N </script></span></p>
</label>
                                                
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                    <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">
                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-147-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>W</mi><mo>=</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>m</mi><msup><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>g</mi><mo>&amp;#x2032;</mo></msup><mo>=</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>m</mi><mo>.</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>g</mi><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mn>1</mn><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mfrac><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>h</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>R</mi></mfrac></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mn>60</mn><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mn>9.8</mn><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mn>1</mn><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mfrac><mn>15</mn><mn>6400</mn></mfrac></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mn>586.62</mn><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>N</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1803" style="width: 26.355em; width: 0px; height: 2.051em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.497em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.652em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mi mathvariant="normal">W</mi><mo>=</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">m</mi><msup><mi mathvariant="normal">g</mi><mo>′</mo></msup><mo>=</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">m</mi><mo>.</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">g</mi><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mn>1</mn><mo>−</mo><mfrac><mi mathvariant="normal">h</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">R</mi></mfrac></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mn>60</mn><mo>×</mo><mn>9.8</mn><mo>×</mo><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mn>1</mn><mo>−</mo><mfrac><mn>15</mn><mn>6400</mn></mfrac></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mn>586.62</mn><mi mathvariant="normal">N</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-147">\rm W=mg'=m.g\ \left(1-\frac{h}{R}\right)=60\times9.8\times\left(1-\frac{15}{6400}\right)=586.62N</script></span></p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div><div class="row questionBlock">

                            <div class="row question">
                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial"><span>Question 45</span></div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p>ভূ-পৃষ্ঠ হতে কত গভীরতায় কোনো বস্তুর ওজন ভূ-পৃষ্ঠের ওজনের 10&nbsp;ভাগের এক ভাগ হবে?</p>

clip: rect(3.24em, 1000.95em, 4.182em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="texatom" id="MathJax-Span-1739"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1740"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1741" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">10</span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.424em; left: 0.986em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1742" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">6</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1743" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">m</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.969em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.647em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 2.002em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mfrac><msup><mi mathvariant="normal">W</mi><mi class="MJX-variant" mathvariant="normal">′</mi></msup><mi mathvariant="normal">W</mi></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>10</mn></mfrac><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><mfrac><msup><mi mathvariant="normal">g</mi><mi class="MJX-variant" mathvariant="normal">′</mi></msup><mi mathvariant="normal">g</mi></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>10</mn></mfrac><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">R</mi><mo>−</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">h</mi></mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">R</mi></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>10</mn></mfrac><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">h</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>9</mn><mn>10</mn></mfrac><mi mathvariant="normal">R</mi><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">h</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>9</mn><mn>10</mn></mfrac><mo>×</mo><mn>6.4</mn><mo>×</mo><msup><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mn>10</mn></mrow><mn>6</mn></msup><mi mathvariant="normal">m</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>5.76</mn><mo>×</mo><msup><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mn>10</mn></mrow><mn>6</mn></msup><mi mathvariant="normal">m</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-120">\rm \frac{W^\prime}{W}=\frac{1}{10}\Rightarrow\frac{g^\prime}{g}=\frac{1}{10}\Rightarrow\frac{R-h}{R}=\frac{1}{10}\Rightarrow h=\frac{9}{10}R\Rightarrow h=\frac{9}{10}\times6.4\times{10}^6m=5.76\times{10}^6m</script></span></p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row questionBlock">

                            <div class="row question">
                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">

                                    <div class="col-sm-12 row questionOption">

                                            <div class="input-group-prepend">
                                                <span class="input-group-text">C</span>
                                            </div>

                                                <label style="margin-left:5px;"><p>যান্ত্রিক শক্তির নিত্যতা সূত্র মানে</p>
</label>
                                                
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>

                                            <div class="input-group-append questionTable">
                                                <label style="margin-left:5px;"><p>মহাকর্ষ বল সংরক্ষণশীল বল</p>
</label>
                                                
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                    <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">
                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p>পূর্ণচক্রে মোট কাজ শূন্য।</p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row questionBlock">

                            <div class="row question">

                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p>কার্যকরী ক্ষমতা,&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-22-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi>P</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>3430</mn><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mn>0.85</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>2915.5</mn><mi>W</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-298" style="width: 12.297em; top: -1.965em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-299"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-300" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">P<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; padding-left: 0.289em;">3430</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-303" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">×</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-304" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">2915.5</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-307" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">W<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.125em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; <p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-23-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mfrac><mrow><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>m</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>g</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>h</mi></mrow><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>t</mi></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>P</mi><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>&amp;#x21D2;</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>m</mi><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mn>9.8</mn><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mn>8</mn></mrow><mn>60</mn></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>2915.5</mn><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>&amp;#x21D2;</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>m</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>2231.25</mn><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>k</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>g</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-308" style="width: 21.15em;                                         <div class="serial"><span>Question 51</span></div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p>একটি পানিপূর্ণ কুয়ার গভীরতা 10 m এবং ব্যাস 1.5 m। একটি<br>
পাম্প 25&nbsp;মিনিটে কুয়াটিকে পানিশূন্য করতে পারে। পাম্পটির ক্ষমতা&nbsp;<br>
কত?</p>

top: -1.227em; left: 0em;"><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: 0em; border-top: 1.5px solid; width: 0.412em; height: 0px;"></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1000.25em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -3.686em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.121em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-364" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">t</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.904em, 1004.14em, 1.191em, -999.998em); top: -1.268em; left: 0em;"><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: 0em; border-top: 1.5px solid; width: 4.141em; height: 0px;"></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-365" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-366" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">0.773</span><span class="mtext" id="MathJax-Span-367" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">&nbsp;</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-368" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">H</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-369" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">P</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.969em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.497em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 2.152em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mi mathvariant="normal">P</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">m</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">g</mi><mfrac><mi mathvariant="normal">h</mi><mn>2</mn></mfrac></mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">t</mi></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi>π</mi><msup><mi mathvariant="normal">r</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mi mathvariant="normal">h</mi><mo>×</mo><mi>ρ</mi><mo>×</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">g</mi><mfrac><mi mathvariant="normal">h</mi><mn>2</mn></mfrac></mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">t</mi></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>0.773</mn><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mi mathvariant="normal">H</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">P</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-24">\rm P=\frac{mg\frac{h}{2}}{t}=\frac{\pi r^2\ h\times\rho\times g\frac{h}{2}}{t}=0.773\ HP </script></span></p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row questionBlock">

                            <div class="row question">
                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">

                                        <div class="serial"><span>Question 52</span></div>

                                    <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">
                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>

</span>

                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-59-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>E</mi><mo>=</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>g</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>4</mn><mn>3</mn></mfrac><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>G</mi><mi>&amp;#x03C0;</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>R</mi><mi>&amp;#x03C1;</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>4.193</mn><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>m</mi><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mo>/</mo></mrow><msup><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>s</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-923" style="width: 13.568em; <p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-60-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2234;</mo><msup><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>g</mi><mi class=&quot;MJX-variant&quot; top: -2.17em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-948"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-949" style="font-family: MathJax_AMS;">∴</span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-950" style="padding-left: 0.289em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.781em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1000.49em, 4.346em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-951" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">g</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.383em; left: 0.494em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-952" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">′</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-953" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-954" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">g</span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-955"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 3.445em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(2.748em, 1002.83em, 4.797em, -999.998em); position: relative; width: 1.6em; height: 0px; margin-right: 0.125em; margin-left: 0.125em;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.404em, 1000.53em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.424em; left: 50%; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.904em, 1001.52em, 1.191em, -999.998em); top: -1.268em; left: 0em;"><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.629em; left: 2.707em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-976" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-977" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-978" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">4.0299</span><span class="mtext" id="MathJax-Span-979" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">&nbsp;</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-980" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">m</span><span class="texatom" id="MathJax-Span-981"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-982"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-983" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">/</span></span></span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-984"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.822em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1000.37em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-985" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">s</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.383em; left: 0.412em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-986" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.174em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.847em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 2.552em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mo>∴</mo><msup><mi mathvariant="normal">g</mi><mi class="MJX-variant" mathvariant="normal">′</mi></msup><mo>=</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">g</mi><msup><mrow><mo>(</mo><mfrac><mi mathvariant="normal">R</mi><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">R</mi><mo>+</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">h</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo>)</mo></mrow><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>=</mo><mn>4.193</mn><mo>×</mo><msup><mrow><mo>(</mo><mfrac><mn>5000</mn><mn>5100</mn></mfrac><mo>)</mo></mrow><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>=</mo><mn>4.0299</mn><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mi mathvariant="normal">m</mi><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mo>/</mo></mrow><msup><mi mathvariant="normal">s</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-60">\rm \therefore g^\prime=g\left(\frac{R}{R+h}\right)^2=4.193\times\left(\frac{5000}{5100}\right)^2=4.0299\ m/s^2</script></span></p>
</span>

                            </div>

                        <div class="row questionBlock">

                            <div class="row question">
                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial"><span>Question 54</span></div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-139-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mn>85</mn><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>N</mi><msup><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>m</mi><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msup></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1937" style="width: 4.696em;                         <div class="row questionBlock">

                            <div class="row question">
                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial"><span>Question 55</span></div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p>120 পাউন্ড ওজনের একজন লোক 90 পাউন্ড ওজনের একটি বস্তুকে অনুভূমিক মেঝের উপর দিয়ে 6&nbsp;ফুট দূরত্বে ঠেলে নিতে 30&nbsp;পাউন্ড ওজনের অনুভূমিক বল প্রয়োগ করেন। কাজের পরিমাণ-</p>

                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="row questionOptions">
                                    <div class="col-sm-12 row questionOption">
                                        <div class="input-group " style="align-items: center;">
                                            <div class="input-group-prepend">
                                                <span class="input-group-text">A</span>
                                            </div>
                                            <div class="input-group-append questionTable">
                                                <label style="margin-left:5px;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-146-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mn>2700</mn><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi>f</mi><mi>t</mi><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mi>l</mi><mi>b</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-2003" style="width: 6.241em;
