width: 0.822em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.404em, 1000.53em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-3454" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">R</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.301em; left: 0.535em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-3455" style="font-size: 50%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.904em, 1001.44em, 1.191em, -999.998em); top: -1.268em; left: 0em;"><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: 0em; border-top: 1.5px solid; width: 1.436em; height: 0px;"></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mtext" id="MathJax-Span-3456" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">&nbsp;</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-3457" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">⇒</span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-3458" style="padding-left: 0.289em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.904em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1000.49em, 4.346em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-3459" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">g<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.002em;"></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -3.85em; left: 0.494em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-3460" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">1</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-3461" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-3462" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">9.72</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-3463" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">m</span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-3464"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.436em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1000.41em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-3465" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">s</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.383em; left: 0.453em;"><span class="texatom" id="MathJax-Span-3466"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-3467"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-3468" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">−</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-3469" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.051em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.698em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.852em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mfrac><msub><mi>g</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mi>g</mi></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>−</mo><mfrac><mi>h</mi><mi>R</mi></mfrac><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><msub><mi>g</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo>=</mo><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mn>1</mn><mo>−</mo><mfrac><mi>h</mi><mi>R</mi></mfrac></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mi>g</mi><mo>=</mo><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mn>1</mn><mo>−</mo><mfrac><mi>h</mi><mi>R</mi></mfrac></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mfrac><mrow><mi>G</mi><mi>M</mi></mrow><msup><mi>R</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></mfrac><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><msub><mi>g</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo>=</mo><mn>9.72</mn><mi>m</mi><msup><mi>s</mi><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mo>−</mo><mn>2</mn></mrow></msup></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-122">\frac{g_1}{g}=1-\frac{h}{R}\Rightarrow g_1=\left(1-\frac{h}{R}\right)g=\left(1-\frac{h}{R}\right)\frac{GM}{R^2}\ \Rightarrow g_1=9.72ms^{-2}</script></span></p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row questionBlock">

                            <div class="row question">
                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial"><span>Question 57</span></div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">

                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-128-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><msup><mi>v</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi>G</mi><mi>M</mi></mrow><mrow><mi>R</mi><mo>+</mo><mi>h</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>&amp;#x21D2;</mo><mi>v</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>5.68</mn><mi>k</mi><mi>m</mi><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mo>/</mo></mrow><mi>s</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-3519" style="width: 11.723em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 9.592em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.945em, 1009.55em, 2.543em, -999.998em); top: -1.965em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-3520"><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-3521"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.904em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1000.45em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-3522" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">v</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.383em; left: 0.494em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-3523" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-3524" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mfrac" id="MathJax-Span-3525" style="padding-left: 0.289em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.6em; height: 0px; margin-right: 0.125em; margin-left: 0.125em;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.404em, 1001.31em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.424em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.654em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-3526"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-3527" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">G</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-3528" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">M<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.043em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.404em, 1001.48em, 4.182em, -999.998em); top: -3.645em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.736em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-3529"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-3530" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">R</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-3531" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">+</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-3532" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">h</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.904em, 1001.6em, 1.191em, -999.998em); top: -1.268em; left: 0em;"><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: 0em; border-top: 1.5px solid; width: 1.6em; height: 0px;"></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-3533" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">⇒</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-3534" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic; padding-left: 0.289em;">v</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-3535" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-3536" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">5.68</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-3537" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">k</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-3538" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">m</span><span class="texatom" id="MathJax-Span-3539"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-3540"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-3541" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">/</span></span></span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-3542" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">s</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.969em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.597em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.752em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><msup><mi>v</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi>G</mi><mi>M</mi></mrow><mrow><mi>R</mi><mo>+</mo><mi>h</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><mi>v</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>5.68</mn><mi>k</mi><mi>m</mi><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mo>/</mo></mrow><mi>s</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-128">v^2=\frac{GM}{R+h}\Rightarrow v=5.68km/s</script></span></p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row questionBlock">

                            <div class="row question">
                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">

                                            <p>একটি বলকে ভূ-পৃষ্ঠের সাথে 60° কোণে উপরে ছুড়ে মারা হল। যদি এটি পৃথিবীতে ফিরে না আসে তাহলে এর আদিবেগ কত ছিল?</p>

                                    </div>

                                    <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">
                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p>আদিবেগ মুক্তিবেগের সমান হতে হবে। এটি কোণের উপর নির্ভর করে না।</p>
</span>

                                                <label style="margin-left:5px;"><p>b &amp; c এর মধ্যে যেকোন মান</p>

                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-141-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><msub><mi>g</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo>=</mo><mi>g</mi><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><msup><mi>&amp;#x03C9;</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mi>R</mi><mi>c</mi><mi>o</mi><msup><mi>s</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mi>&amp;#x03B8;</mi><mo>;</mo></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-3734" style="width: 8.363em;                                     <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">
                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-149-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi>V</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi>G</mi><mi>M</mi><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mn>3</mn><msup><mi>a</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><msup><mi>r</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow></mrow><mrow><mn>2</mn><msup><mi>a</mi><mn>3</mn></msup></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>284</mn><mi>G</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-3818" style="width: 11.846em; padding-left: 0.289em;">−</span><span class="mfrac" id="MathJax-Span-3823"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 4.264em; height: 0px; margin-right: 0.125em; margin-left: 0.125em;"><span style="position: absolute; </span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div><div class="row questionBlock">

<p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-71-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>&amp;#x21D2;</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mrow><mn>8550</mn><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><msup><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mn>10</mn></mrow><mn>3</mn></msup></mrow></mfrac><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mrow /></mfrac><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><msub><mi>r</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></mrow><mo>=</mo><mn>1.67</mn><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><msup><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mn>10</mn></mrow><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>9</mn></mrow></msup></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1108" style="width: 13.773em; top: -1.965em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1109"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1110" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">⇒</span><span class="mfrac" id="MathJax-Span-1111" style="padding-left: 0.289em;"><span style="display: inline-block;                                         <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-158-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi>&amp;#x03C9;</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>2</mn><mi>&amp;#x03C0;</mi></mrow><mi>T</mi></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>2</mn><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mn>3.14</mn></mrow><mn>86400</mn></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>7.3</mn><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><msup><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mn>10</mn></mrow><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>5</mn></mrow></msup><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi>r</mi><mi>a</mi><mi>d</mi><msup><mi>s</mi><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msup></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-3987" style="width: 16.027em;                             <div class="row question">
                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial"><span>Question 65</span></div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p>ক্রেনের সাহায্যে&nbsp;200&nbsp;kg&nbsp;ভরের একটি বস্তুকে&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-159-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mn>0.1</mn><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi>m</mi><msup><mi>s</mi><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msup></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-4024" style="width: 4.734em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 3.877em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.306em, 1003.88em, 2.386em, -999.998em); top: -2.234em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-4025"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-4026" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">0.1</span><span class="mtext" id="MathJax-Span-4027" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">&nbsp;</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-4028" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">m</span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-4029"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.455em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.43em, 1000.41em, 4.1em, -999.998em); top: -3.985em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-4030" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">s</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 3.988em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.357em; left: 0.486em;"><span class="texatom" id="MathJax-Span-4031"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-4032"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-4033" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">−</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-4034" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">1</span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 3.988em;"></span></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; font-family: MathJax_Main;">1</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.01em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.867em, 1001.46em, 1.186em, -999.998em); h=\frac{nx}{n+1} </script></span></p>
</label>
                                                
                                            </div>
                                        </div>

padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mfrac" id="MathJax-Span-4168" style="padding-left: 0.289em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.436em; height: 0px; margin-right: 0.125em; margin-left: 0.125em;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.404em, 1000.82em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.424em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.408em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-4169"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-4170" style="font-size: 70.7%; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1001.27em, 4.182em, -999.998em); top: -3.645em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.654em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-4172"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-4173" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">(</span><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-4184"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-4185" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">n</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-4186" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">+</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-4187" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">1</span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-4188" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">)</span></span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-4189" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">x</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.568em, 1000.41em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -3.686em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.203em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-4190" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">n</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.904em, 1002.42em, 1.191em, -999.998em); top: -1.268em; left: 0em;"><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: 0em; border-top: 1.5px solid; width: 2.42em; height: 0px;"></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -2.698em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 3.702em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><msub><mi>E</mi><mi>K</mi></msub><mo>=</mo><mi>n</mi><msub><mi>E</mi><mi>P</mi></msub><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><mi>m</mi><mi>g</mi><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mi>n</mi><mi>m</mi><mi>g</mi><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mi>h</mi><mo>−</mo><mi>x</mi></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mspace linebreak="newline"></mspace><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mi>n</mi><mi>h</mi><mo>−</mo><mi>n</mi><mi>x</mi><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi>n</mi><mi>h</mi></mrow><mrow><mi>n</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></mfrac><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><mi>h</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mi>n</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mi>x</mi></mrow><mi>n</mi></mfrac></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-170">E_K=nE_P\Rightarrow mgx=nmg\left(h-x\right)\\ \Rightarrow x=nh-nx\ \Rightarrow x=\frac{nh}{n+1}\ \Rightarrow h=\frac{\left(n+1\right)x}{n}  </script></span></p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row questionBlock">

                            <div class="row question">
                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial"><span>Question 67</span></div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p>একটা বস্তুকে&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-171-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>(</mo><mi>&amp;#x03B1;</mi><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mover><mi>i</mi><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>&amp;#x005E;</mo></mover></mrow><mo>+</mo><mn>2</mn><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mover><mi>j</mi><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>&amp;#x005E;</mo></mover></mrow><mo>+</mo><mn>4</mn><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mover><mi>k</mi><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>&amp;#x005E;</mo></mover></mrow><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>)</mo><mi>N</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-4191" style="width: 8.869em; id="MathJax-Element-175">\vec{F}=\alpha\hat{i}+2\hat{j}+4\hat{k} \\ \vec{r}=\left(6-2\right)\hat{i}+\left(8-\alpha\right)\hat{j}+\left(3\alpha-4\right)\hat{k} \\ W=\vec{F}\cdot\vec{r}=4\alpha+16-2\alpha+12\alpha-16=14\alpha \\ \therefore14\alpha=42\Rightarrow\alpha=3 </script></span></p>

width: 0px; height: 1.969em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.348em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.302em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mo>=</mo><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mn>1</mn><mo>−</mo><mn>0.2</mn></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mi>E</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>0.8</mn><mi>E</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-177">=\left(1-0.2\right)E=0.8E </script></span></p>

<p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-178-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mn>0.8</mn><mi>E</mi><mo>=</mo><mi>m</mi><mi>g</mi><msup><mi>h</mi><mi class=&quot;MJX-variant&quot; mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>&amp;#x2032;</mi></msup><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>&amp;#x21D2;</mo><mi>m</mi><mi>g</mi><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mn>80</mn><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mn>0.8</mn><mo>=</mo><mi>m</mi><mi>g</mi><msup><mi>h</mi><mi class=&quot;MJX-variant&quot; mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>&amp;#x2032;</mi></msup><mo>&amp;#x2234;</mo><msup><mi>h</mi><mi class=&quot;MJX-variant&quot; mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>&amp;#x2032;</mi></msup><mo>=</mo><mn>64</mn><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi>m</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-4382" style="width: 22.42em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 18.363em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.273em, 1018.32em, 2.502em, -999.998em); top: -2.17em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-4383"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-4384" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">0.8</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-4385" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">E<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.043em;"></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-4386" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-4387" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic; padding-left: 0.289em;">m</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-4388" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">g<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.002em;"></span></span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-4389"><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.383em; left: 0.576em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-4391" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">′</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-4392" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">⇒</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-4393" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic; padding-left: 0.289em;">m</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-4394" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">g<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.002em;"></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-4395" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">×</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-4396" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">80</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-4397" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">×</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-4398" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">0.8</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-4399" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-4400" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic; padding-left: 0.289em;">m</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-4401" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">g<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.002em;"></span></span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-4402"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.863em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.383em; left: 0.576em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-4404" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">′</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-4405" style="font-family: MathJax_AMS; padding-left: 0.289em;">∴</span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-4406" style="padding-left: 0.289em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.863em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.199em, 1000.58em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-4407" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">h</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.383em; left: 0.576em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-4408" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">′</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-4409" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-4410" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">64</span><span class="mtext" id="MathJax-Span-4411" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">&nbsp;</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-4412" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">m</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.174em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.297em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.302em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mn>0.8</mn><mi>E</mi><mo>=</mo><mi>m</mi><mi>g</mi><msup><mi>h</mi><mi class="MJX-variant" mathvariant="normal">′</mi></msup><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><mi>m</mi><mi>g</mi><mo>×</mo><mn>80</mn><mo>×</mo><mn>0.8</mn><mo>=</mo><mi>m</mi><mi>g</mi><msup><mi>h</mi><mi class="MJX-variant" mathvariant="normal">′</mi></msup><mo>∴</mo><msup><mi>h</mi><mi class="MJX-variant" mathvariant="normal">′</mi></msup><mo>=</mo><mn>64</mn><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mi>m</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-178">0.8E=mgh^\prime\Rightarrow mg\times80\times0.8=mgh^\prime\therefore h^\prime=64\ m </script></span></p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row questionBlock">

                            <div class="row question">
                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial"><span>Question 69</span></div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p>h&nbsp;উচ্চতা হতে কোনো একটি বস্তুকে ছেড়ে দেওয়া হলো। প্রতিবার মাটিতে আঘাত করার ফলে বস্তুটি 50% করে বিভব শক্তি হারায়। বস্তু কর্তৃক অতিক্রান্ত মোট দূরত্ব কত?</p>

font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.904em, 1000.37em, 1.191em, -999.998em); top: -1.227em; left: 0em;"><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: 0em; border-top: 1.5px solid; width: 0.371em; height: 0px;"></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.904em, 1001.64em, 1.191em, -999.998em); width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-4485" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-4486" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">3</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-4487" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">h</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.051em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -1.047em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 2.202em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mo>=</mo><mi>h</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>2</mn><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mfrac><mi>h</mi><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mo>+</mo><mfrac><mi>h</mi><mn>4</mn></mfrac><mo>+</mo><mfrac><mi>h</mi><mn>8</mn></mfrac><mo>+</mo><mo>…</mo></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mi>h</mi><mo>+</mo><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mi>h</mi><mo>+</mo><mfrac><mi>h</mi><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mo>+</mo><mfrac><mi>h</mi><mn>4</mn></mfrac><mo>+</mo><mo>…</mo></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mi>h</mi><mo>+</mo><mfrac><mi>h</mi><mrow><mn>1</mn><mo>−</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>3</mn><mi>h</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-184">=h+2\ \left(\frac{h}{2}+\frac{h}{4}+\frac{h}{8}+\ldots\right)=h+\left(h+\frac{h}{2}+\frac{h}{4}+\ldots\right)=h+\frac{h}{1-\frac{1}{2}}=3h   </script></span></p>
</span>
                                    </div>

                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial"><span>Question 70</span></div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p>ভূমি হতে উল্লম্বভাবে উপরে নিক্ষিপ্ত বস্তুর গতিশক্তি&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-185-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>(</mo><msub><mi>E</mi><mi>k</mi></msub><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>)</mo></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-4488" style="width: 2.424em; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.039em;"></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 3.988em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -3.836em; left: 0.747em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-4493" style="font-size: 70.7%;                                     <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">
                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p>উপরে নিক্ষিপ্ত হলে প্রথমে বেগ কমবে এবং সর্বোচ্চ উচ্চতায় শূন্য হয়ে আবার নিচে পড়া শুরু করবে। তখন গতিশক্তি আবার বৃদ্ধি পাবে অর্থাৎ&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-186-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><msub><mi>E</mi><mi>k</mi></msub><mo>&amp;#x221D;</mo><msup><mi>v</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>&amp;#x221D;</mo><msup><mi>t</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-4495" style="width: 5.617em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 4.592em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.027em, 1004.59em, 2.256em, -999.998em); top: -1.965em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-4496"><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-4497"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.191em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.199em, 1000.78em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-4498" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">E<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.043em;"></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -3.85em; left: 0.74em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-4499" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">k</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-4500" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">∝</span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-4501" style="padding-left: 0.289em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.904em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1000.45em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-4502" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">v</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.383em; left: 0.494em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-4503" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-4504" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">∝</span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-4505" style="padding-left: 0.289em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.781em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.281em, 1000.33em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-4506" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">t</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.383em; left: 0.371em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-4507" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.969em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.247em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.302em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><msub><mi>E</mi><mi>k</mi></msub><mo>∝</mo><msup><mi>v</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>∝</mo><msup><mi>t</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-186">E_k\propto v^2\propto t^2</script></span>&nbsp;হবে।</p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div><div class="row questionBlock">

                            <div class="row question">
                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial"><span>Question 71</span></div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p style="text-align: justify;">একটি বস্তুকণা স্থিরাবস্থা থেকে অভিকর্ষের প্রভাবে পড়তে থাকে। ভূপৃষ্ঠের সাপেক্ষে কণাটির স্থিতিশক্তি (PE) ও গতিশক্তি (KE) এবং সময় (t) এর লেখচিত্র আঁকা হলো। সঠিক লেখচিত্র কোনটি?</p>

                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="row questionOptions">
                                    <div class="col-sm-12 row questionOption">
                                        <div class="input-group " style="align-items: center;">
                                            <div class="input-group-prepend">
                                                <span class="input-group-text">A</span>
                                            </div>
                                            <div class="input-group-append questionTable">
                                                <label style="margin-left:5px;"><p><img alt="" src="data:image/png;base64," style="height: 78px; width: 70px;"></p>
</label>
                                                
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="col-sm-12 row questionOption">
                                        <div class="input-group " style="align-items: center;">
                                            <div class="input-group-prepend">
                                                <span class="input-group-text">B</span>
                                            </div>
                                            <div class="input-group-append questionTable">
                                                <label style="margin-left:5px;"><p><img alt="" src="data:image/png;base64," style="width: 80px; height: 74px;"></p>
</label>
                                                
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="col-sm-12 row questionOption">
                                        <div class="input-group " style="align-items: center;">
                                            <div class="input-group-prepend">
                                                <span class="input-group-text">C</span>
                                            </div>

position: relative; width: 0.945em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1000.49em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-162" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">v</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.383em; left: 0.535em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-163" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-164" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mfrac" id="MathJax-Span-165" style="padding-left: 0.289em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.494em; height: 0px; margin-right: 0.125em; margin-left: 0.125em;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1000.29em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.424em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.162em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-166" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">1</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1000.33em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -3.645em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.162em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-167" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.904em, 1000.49em, 1.191em, -999.998em); top: -1.268em; left: 0em;"><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: 0em; border-top: 1.5px solid; width: 0.494em; height: 0px;"></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-168" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">m</span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-169"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.945em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1000.49em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-170" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">v</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1000.41em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.342em; left: 0.535em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-171" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1000.41em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -3.727em; left: 0.535em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-172" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">1</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-173" style="font-family: MathJax_AMS; padding-left: 0.289em;">∴</span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-174" style="padding-left: 0.289em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.945em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1000.49em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-175" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">v</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -3.85em; left: 0.535em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-176" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">1</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-177" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-178" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">3</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-179" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">v</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.174em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.497em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.602em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mo>∴</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">m</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">a</mi><mo>×</mo><mn>9</mn><mi mathvariant="normal">h</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mi mathvariant="normal">m</mi><msubsup><mi mathvariant="normal">v</mi><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></msubsup><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><mn>9</mn><mo>×</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mi mathvariant="normal">m</mi><msup><mi mathvariant="normal">v</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mi mathvariant="normal">m</mi><msubsup><mi mathvariant="normal">v</mi><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></msubsup><mo>∴</mo><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">v</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo>=</mo><mn>3</mn><mi mathvariant="normal">v</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-5">\rm \therefore ma\times9h=\frac{1}{2}mv_1^2\Rightarrow9\times\frac{1}{2}mv^2=\frac{1}{2}mv_1^2\therefore v_1=3v</script></span></p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row questionBlock">

                            <div class="row question">
                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial"><span>Question 75</span></div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p>একটি 500 gm ভরের বস্তুকে ভূমি থেকে নির্দিষ্ট উচ্চতায় উঠালে এতে 16 J বিভবশক্তি সঞ্চিত হয়। বস্তুটিকে ঐ উচ্চতা থেকে ছেড়ে দিলে এটি ভূমিতে কত বেগে আঘাত করবে?</p>

                                        </div>

                                    <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">
                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-10-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>m</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>g</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>h</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><msup><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>m</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>v</mi></mrow><mn>2</mn></msup><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>&amp;#x21D2;</mo><mn>16</mn><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mn>0.5</mn><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><msup><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>v</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>&amp;#x2234;</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>v</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>8</mn><msup><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>m</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>s</mi></mrow><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msup></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-232" style="width: 20.904em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 17.133em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.191em, 1017.13em, 2.666em, -999.998em); top: -2.17em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-233"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-234" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">m</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-235" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">g</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-236" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">h</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-237" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mfrac" id="MathJax-Span-238" style="padding-left: 0.289em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.494em; height: 0px; margin-right: 0.125em; margin-left: 0.125em;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1000.29em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.424em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.162em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-239" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">1</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1000.33em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -3.645em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.162em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-240" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.904em, 1000.49em, 1.191em, -999.998em); top: -1.268em; left: 0em;"><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: 0em; border-top: 1.5px solid; width: 0.494em; height: 0px;"></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-241"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.805em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1001.36em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="texatom" id="MathJax-Span-242"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-243"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-244" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">m</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-245" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">v</span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.383em; left: 1.355em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-246" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-247" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">⇒</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-248" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">16</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-249" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mfrac" id="MathJax-Span-250" style="padding-left: 0.289em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.494em; height: 0px; margin-right: 0.125em; margin-left: 0.125em;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1000.29em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.424em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.162em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-251" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">1</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1000.33em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -3.645em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.162em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-252" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.904em, 1000.49em, 1.191em, -999.998em); top: -1.268em; left: 0em;"><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: 0em; border-top: 1.5px solid; width: 0.494em; height: 0px;"></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-253" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">×</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-254" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">0.5</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-255" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">×</span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-256" style="padding-left: 0.207em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.945em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1000.49em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-257" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">v</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.383em; left: 0.535em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-258" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-259" style="font-family: MathJax_AMS; padding-left: 0.289em;">∴</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-260" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">v</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-261" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-262" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">8</span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-263"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 2.215em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1001.19em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="texatom" id="MathJax-Span-264"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-265"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-266" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">m</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-267" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">s</span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.383em; left: 1.232em;"><span class="texatom" id="MathJax-Span-268"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-269"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-270" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">−</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-271" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">1</span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.174em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.497em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.602em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mi mathvariant="normal">m</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">g</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">h</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><msup><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mi mathvariant="normal">m</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">v</mi></mrow><mn>2</mn></msup><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><mn>16</mn><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mo>×</mo><mn>0.5</mn><mo>×</mo><msup><mi mathvariant="normal">v</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>∴</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">v</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>8</mn><msup><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mi mathvariant="normal">m</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">s</mi></mrow><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msup></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-10">\rm mgh=\frac{1}{2}{\rm mv}^2\Rightarrow16=\frac{1}{2}\times0.5\times v^2\therefore v=8{\rm ms}^{-1}  </script></span></p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row questionBlock">

                                    <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">
                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-15-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>P</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>m</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>g</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>s</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>c</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>o</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>s</mi><mi>&amp;#x03B8;</mi></mrow><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>t</mi></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>20</mn><mo>&amp;#xD7;</mo><mn>9.8</mn><mo>&amp;#xD7;</mo><mn>2</mn><mo>&amp;#xD7;</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>c</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>o</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>s</mi><mn>60</mn><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mo>&amp;#xB0;</mo></mrow></mrow><mn>9.8</mn></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>20</mn><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mn>2</mn><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>20</mn><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>W</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-292" style="width: 21.682em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 17.748em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.822em, 1017.75em, 2.461em, -999.998em); top: -1.965em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-293"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-294" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">P</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-295" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mfrac" id="MathJax-Span-296" style="padding-left: 0.289em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 2.625em; height: 0px; margin-right: 0.125em; clip: rect(0.904em, 1002.62em, 1.191em, -999.998em); top: -1.268em; left: 0em;"><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: 0em; border-top: 1.5px solid; width: 2.625em; height: 0px;"></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1000.86em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -3.645em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.449em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-322" style="font-size: 70.7%; width: 0px; height: 1.969em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.497em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.802em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mi mathvariant="normal">P</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">m</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">g</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">s</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">c</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">o</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">s</mi><mi>θ</mi></mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">t</mi></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>20</mn><mo>×</mo><mn>9.8</mn><mo>×</mo><mn>2</mn><mo>×</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">c</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">o</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">s</mi><mn>60</mn><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mo>°</mo></mrow></mrow><mn>9.8</mn></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>20</mn><mo>×</mo><mn>2</mn><mo>×</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>20</mn><mi mathvariant="normal">W</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-15">\rm P=\frac{mgscos\theta}{t}=\frac{20×9.8×2×cos60°}{9.8}=20\times2\times\frac{1}{2}=20W</script></span></p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        
                        <div class="row questionBlock">

\frac{F_1}{F_2}=\frac{1}{2}\ \therefore F_2=2F_1 </script></span></p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

padding-left: 0.289em;">:</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-512" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">y</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-513" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-514" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">1</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-515" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">:</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-516" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">2</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.174em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.497em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.652em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mi mathvariant="normal">g</mi><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mn>1</mn><mo>−</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>2</mn><mi mathvariant="normal">x</mi></mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">R</mi></mfrac></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">g</mi><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mn>1</mn><mo>−</mo><mfrac><mi mathvariant="normal">y</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">R</mi></mfrac></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>2</mn><mi mathvariant="normal">x</mi></mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">R</mi></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mi mathvariant="normal">y</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">R</mi></mfrac><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mo>∴</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">x</mi><mo>:</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">y</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>:</mo><mn>2</mn></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-21">\rm g\left(1-\frac{2x}{R}\right)=g\left(1-\frac{y}{R}\right)\Rightarrow\frac{2x}{R}=\frac{y}{R}\ \therefore x:y=1:2 </script></span></p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row questionBlock">

                            <div class="row question">
                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial"><span>Question 79</span></div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-22-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mfrac><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>g</mi><mn>4</mn></mfrac></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-517" style="width: 0.859em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.71em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.269em, 1000.71em, 2.722em, -999.998em); top: -2.234em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-518"><span class="mfrac" id="MathJax-Span-519"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.486em; height: 0px; margin-right: 0.114em; top: -3.612em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.184em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-521" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">4</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 3.988em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute;                                     <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">
                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-23-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>W</mi><mo>=</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>m</mi><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>g</mi><mo>+</mo><mfrac><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>g</mi><mn>4</mn></mfrac></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>5</mn><mn>4</mn></mfrac><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mn>80</mn><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mn>9.8</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>980</mn><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>N</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-522" style="width: 17.133em; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mfrac" id="MathJax-Span-537" style="padding-left: 0.289em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.494em; height: 0px; margin-right: 0.125em; margin-left: 0.125em;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1000.33em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.424em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.162em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-538" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">5</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.404em, 1000.33em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -3.645em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.162em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-539" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">4</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.904em, 1000.49em, 1.191em, -999.998em); top: -1.268em; left: 0em;"><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: 0em; border-top: 1.5px solid; width: 0.494em; height: 0px;"></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-540" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">×</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-541" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">80</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-542" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">×</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-543" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">9.8</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-544" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-545" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">980</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-546" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">N</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.051em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.497em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.602em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mi mathvariant="normal">W</mi><mo>=</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">m</mi><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">g</mi><mo>+</mo><mfrac><mi mathvariant="normal">g</mi><mn>4</mn></mfrac></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>5</mn><mn>4</mn></mfrac><mo>×</mo><mn>80</mn><mo>×</mo><mn>9.8</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>980</mn><mi mathvariant="normal">N</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-23">\rm W=m\left(g+\frac{g}{4}\right)=\frac{5}{4}\times80\times9.8=980N </script></span></p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>

                        <div class="row questionBlock">

                            <div class="row question">
                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial"><span>Question 85</span></div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p>নিচের তথ্যগুলো লক্ষ কর–<br>
(i) সমান গতিশক্তির দু’টি বস্তুর মাঝে হালকা বস্তুর বেগ বেশি<br>
(ii) গতিশক্তি ঋণাত্মক হবে যদি বেগ বিপরীত দিকে হয়<br>
(iii) গতিশক্তি <span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-13-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><msup><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>m</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>v</mi></mrow><mn>2</mn></msup></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-208" style="width: 4.324em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 3.541em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.269em, 1003.54em, 2.684em, -999.998em); top: -2.234em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-209"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-210" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">=</span><span class="mfrac" id="MathJax-Span-211" style="padding-left: 0.263em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.486em; height: 0px; margin-right: 0.114em; margin-left: 0.114em;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.392em, 1000.3em, 4.1em, -999.998em); top: -4.395em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.184em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-212" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">1</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 3.988em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.392em, 1000.34em, 4.1em, -999.998em); top: -3.649em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.184em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-213" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 3.988em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.859em, 1000.49em, 1.157em, -999.998em); top: -1.265em; left: 0em;"><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: 0em; border-top: 1.6px solid; width: 0.486em; height: 0px;"></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.045em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-214"><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 3.988em;"></span></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.237em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; <strong>নিচের কোনটি সঠিক?</strong></p>

                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p>শক্তির নিত্যতা সূত্র অনুযায়ী মোট শক্তি সর্বদা একই থাকে।</p>

একটি পানিপূর্ণ কুয়ার গভীরতা 12m এবং ব্যাস 2m। একটি পাম্প 20 মিনিটে কুয়াটিকে পানিশূন্য করতে পারে।</p>

<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-26-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2234;</mo></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-426" style="width: 0.658em; সময় সাশ্রয় হবে <span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-27-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>(</mo><mn>20</mn><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>16.67</mn><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>)</mo></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-429" style="width: 5.248em; </span>
                                    </div>

                        <div class="row questionBlock">

                            <div class="row question">
                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial"><span>Question 97</span></div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p>কোনো বল কর্তৃক কৃতকাজ–<br>
(i) বল এবং সরণের ডটগুণন<br>
(ii) বল <span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-16-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-300" style="width: 0.971em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.784em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.641em, 1000.63em, 2.349em, -999.998em); top: -2.234em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-301"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-302" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">×</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.237em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.043em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 0.684em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mo>×</mo></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-16">\times</script></span> ত্বরণ<br>
(iii) গতিশক্তির পরিবর্তনের সমান<br>
<strong>নিচের কোনটি সঠিক?</strong></p>

                                        </div>
                                    </div>
